quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  26,207,"Ko honﾉ蓉m nafi ﾉ兎 ﾉ擁n neemaaji ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 wonunoo e muuﾉ蓉m ka aduna?! Gomﾉ擁i ﾉ擁n neemaaji taﾆｴii, ﾉ蓉m nafaali hay e huunde."
  26,208,"Men halkataa mofte woo si wanaa ﾉ殿awo ngantinirgol e majje nulugol Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e jippinngol defte ﾉ容n."
  26,209,"Waaju e anndintingol ﾉ兎, Men wonaali tooﾃｱirﾉ兎 leptugol ﾉ兎 ﾉ殿awo ngantinorgol e maﾉ橡兎 nulugol Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e jippinngol defte ﾉ容n."
  26,210,"Seytanuuji ﾉ擁n jippinaali ndee Alqur'aanaare ka ﾉ兎rnde Nulaaﾉ熔 on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna)."
  26,211,"Sellataa nde ﾉ擁 jippinta ka ﾉ兎rnde makko, wurin ﾉ擁 hattanaaka ﾉ蓉m."
  26,212,"ﾆ格 hattantaake ﾉ蓉m, sabu kannji ko ﾉ擁 woﾉ遼擁nti- naaﾉ擁 gaayi nokku mayre on immorde ka kammu, ko honno ﾉ擁 yottorta e mayre, sakko ﾉ擁 jippina nde?!"
  26,213,"Wata a rewu wonndude e Alla reweteeﾉ熔 goo kafidaa mo e Makko, sakko wonaa sabu ﾉ蓉m jeyaaﾉ熔 e leptoyteeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  26,214,"Jertin -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 ﾉ殿daade refti ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 ﾉ殿daade ka yimﾉ兎 maaﾉ預, fii wata heﾉ砥 ﾉ兎 Lepte Alla si ﾉ兎 heddike e dow sirku ngun."
  26,215,"Newinan banﾅ菊 maaﾉ預 konngol e kuugal wonan- nde ﾉ兎n jokkuﾉ兎 ma immorde e gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka yurminngol ﾉ兎 newanoo ﾉ兎."
  26,216,"Si ﾉ兎 yeddii ma, hara ﾉ兎 jaabaaki ko yamirﾉ預aﾉ兎 kon e muuﾉ蓉m immorde e Ngootimbaaku Alla e ﾉ熔ftagol Mo, haray maakan ﾉ兎: Min dey, ko mi pottitiiﾉ熔 kon ko golloton immorde e sirku ngun e geddi ﾉ擁n."
  26,217,"Tuugo e fiyakuuji maaﾉ擁n fow e On Tedduﾉ熔 yoﾉ鍍otooﾉ熔 ayﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, Yurmeteeﾉ熔 ﾉ兎n ruttiiﾉ兎 e maﾉ橡兎 faade ka Makko."
  26,218,"On sutiiﾉ熔 ma O Senike fewndo darantoﾉ預a Julde nden."
  26,219,"Seniiﾉ熔 On no sutii waylitagol maaﾉ預 iwa e alahaali yaha e alhaali goo e hakkude juulooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎, suuﾉ預naaki Mo hay huunde e ko waﾉ預taa kon, wanaa kadi ko tanaa maaﾉ預 waﾉ預ta kon."
  26,220,"Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo ko janngataa kon immorde e Alqur'aana e jaﾅ逆a ka nder Julde maaﾉ預, Annduﾉ熔 On, annuyee maaﾉ預."
  26,221,"Taw si on accay mi humpita on, ko e hoore hommbo Seytanuuji ﾉ擁n jippotoo, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 aaﾆｴiﾉ熔n wonndema kannji ﾉ擁 jippinii ndee Alqur'aanaare?"
  26,222,"Seytanuuji ﾉ擁n no jippoo e dow kala heewuﾉ熔 penaale ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 bakkaatu e geddi immorde e ndureeﾉ兎(wageebe) ﾉ兎n."
  26,223,"Seytanuuji ﾉ擁n no wujja nanﾉ容 ﾉ容n immorde ka mbatu ﾉ砥rngu toowude, ﾉ擁 werlo ﾉ蓉m faade e weldiiﾉ兎 majji immorde e ndureeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 heewude e ndureeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko ﾉ兎 fenooﾉ兎, hay si ﾉ兎 goongii e nder konngol, ﾉ兎 fenay ﾉ兎 wattida e maggol penaale teemedere."
  26,224,"ﾆ‘n yimooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 aaﾆｴiﾉ熔n wonndema Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) ko jeyaaﾉ熔 e maﾉ橡兎, ko jokki ﾉ兎n, ko seluﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n peewal ngal e laawol focciingol ngol, hiﾉ兎 fillitoo ko ﾉ兎n wowlata kon immorde e gimi."
  26,225,"Kaa a tinaali -an Nulaaﾉ熔- wonndema no jeyaa e feeﾃｱirde bewre maﾉ橡兎 nden wonnde kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 wemmboo e nder kala aynde nde ﾉ兎 feﾆｴﾆｴi, tuma goo e mantugol, tumagoo kadi e ﾅ喫ﾃｱugol, e tanaa majji kannji ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 tumagoo kadi."
  26,226,"E tawde kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 fena, ﾉ兎 wi'a: Men waﾉ擁i huunde kaari, hara ﾉ兎 waﾉ預ali nde."
  26,227,"Si wanaa ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 immorde e yimooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 golli golle moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 jaﾅ逆ii Alla jaﾅ逆agol heewungol, ﾉ兎 fooli ayﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎n ﾉ殿awo ﾉ兎 tooﾃｱii ﾉ兎 wano Hassaanu geﾉ預l Saabitu (yo Alla weltor mo). ﾆ‘n tooﾃｱirﾉ兎 sirkanngol Alla e jaggitugol e hoore jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, aray ka ﾉ兎 annda ko hennde e ruttorde ﾉ兎 ruttotoo faade e muuﾉ蓉m, aray ﾉ兎 ruttoo faade e darorde mawnde, e hasboore sewunde."